Name: test_multi_obstacle_navigation
Description: NEW: Test that the robot navigates and stops at the first of multiple obstacles.

Name: test_arm_safety_on_multiple_moves
Description: Test that the arm never goes below safe threshold after multiple moves.

Name: test_navigation_to_multiple_waypoints
Description: Test that the robot can follow multiple waypoints in sequence.

Name: test_full_pick_and_place_sequence
Description: Test the complete pick and place action.

Name: test_navigation_boundary_limit
Description: Test that the robot does not cross the boundary (x <= 1.0).

Name: test_pick_fail_then_retry
Description: Test that a failed pick attempt can be retried successfully.

Name: test_carry_and_place_on_elevated_target
Description: Test that the robot carries a cube and places it on an elevated surface.

Name: test_walk_and_pick_sequence
Description: Test the combined walking and picking action.

Name: test_robot_walks_while_holding_object
Description: Test a full scenario: the robot picks up a cube and carries it to a new location.

Name: test_pick_and_place_without_arm
Description: Test that a RuntimeError is raised when trying to pick and place without an arm.

Name: test_carry_object_through_obstacle
Description: Test that the robot carrying an object stops before an obstacle.

Name: test_sequential_pick_and_drop
Description: NEW: Test the robot's ability to pick up and drop multiple objects in sequence.

Name: test_full_navigation_obstacle_avoidance
Description: Test that the robot stops before an obstacle during navigation.

Name: test_place_on_elevated_surface
Description: NEW: Test that the robot can move an object to a higher elevation.

Name: test_navigation_target_before_obstacle
Description: NEW: Test that the robot correctly reaches a target that is before an obstacle.

Name: test_full_navigation_to_target
Description: Test that the robot navigates to a target position correctly.

Name: test_move_arm_below_safe_height
Description: Test that the arm cannot move below a safe height.

Name: test_pick_move_and_place_full_cycle
Description: NEW: Test picking up an object, walking to a new location, and placing it.

Name: test_robot_returns_to_origin
Description: Test that the robot can walk away and attempt to return to origin (no backward walking).

Name: test_pick_and_place_two_objects
Description: Test picking and placing two different objects sequentially.

Name: test_pick_abort_no_object_moved
Description: Test that an object's position is not changed if the gripper fails to close.
